Package assignment05_000921540

Class Factory

java.lang.Object
assignment05_000921540.Factory
public class Factory extends Object
The Brain for the Factory game. The Factory class contains references to Upgrades, Workers, and Pickaxe types. Within the Factory, all of our processing occurs.
